  str_replace_all("\\t", "")

flowers_tidy

flowers_tidy <- flowers_tidy%>%
  group_by(genus, species)%>%
  summarize(mean_length = mean(cor_length), mean_width = mean(throat_width), max_length = max(cor_length), max_width = max(throat_width))
flowers_tidy
